d oversikt p\u00e5 hva du har brukt penger p\u00e5.", "- Bruk de siste tiden p\u00e5 \u00e5 se etter tilbudsvarer. Venter du til lille julaften eller timene f\u00f8r stengetid p\u00e5 julaften med \u00e5 impulshandle, kan \u00e5rets julegavehandel fort bli en sv\u00e6rt kostbar aff\u00e6re.", "Gode kupp kan du derimot gj\u00f8re p\u00e5 Toilldag."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|okonomi"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "e9ddb28e73c1763648a2ea36ae2622295c3dad4695a2a7b0df6a137160a05c31"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-10-13T00:01:14.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "D\u00e5rlige \u00f8konomiske tider til tross, vi handler til jul som aldri f\u00f8r."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/nyheter/okonomi/article11912151.ece/pjrgjj/ALTERNATES/w980-default/ta152587.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/097e9602d40006971db52f871c9cafb9cb510450.jpg?5920a57c"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Heftig julehandel -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "097e9602d40006971db52f871c9cafb9cb510450"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["\u00f8konomi", "finans", "aksjer", "skatt", "b\u00f8rs", "\u00f8konominyheter"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "\u00f8konomi,finans,aksjer,skatt,b\u00f8rs,\u00f8konominyheter"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "okonomi"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "personal-finance"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["bruk", "handler", "gave", "penger", "julehandel", "kj\u00f8p"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["toilldag", "handelsorganisasjonen virke", "black friday", "danske bank"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "gallup"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": "maria setsaas"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy